<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
               body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: rgb(1, 1, 109);
            color: #dec1ff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            /* background-color: #dec1ff !important; */
            color: #dec1ff;
            
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: rgb(1, 1, 109);
            color: #dec1ff;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Product Rejected! 😕</h1>
            <p>Dear <%= firstName %>,</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Thank you for your interest in selling on Nana's Pourfection Hub.</p>
            <p>Your product has been reviewed and <strong>rejected</strong> by our admin team. Please make the necessary changes and resubmit for review.</p>

            <div class="product-box">
                <h2><%= productName %></h2>
                <p>✗ Rejected</p>
            </div>

            <p>Keep adding more products to grow your store. Remember, each product goes through a quick review before going live.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Nana's Pourfection Hub Team</p>
        </div>
          <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Nana's Pourfection Hub. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>